  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the relative effectiveness of three different
      mental health counseling interventions in the treatment of mental health problems commonly
      affecting torture and trauma survivors living in Kurdistan, Iraq.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      See above
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
